{"tid":1559781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認清楚局勢 黃藍紅 三絲鼎立","createTime":"2019-09-11T03:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T08:25:45.000Z","uid":206298,"like":52,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"05b3a41e08cf5d33f96747d775a7f6f0bd0714b5","tid":1559781,"uid":206298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:12:10.000Z","msg":"黃絲 大家都好清楚<br />\n藍絲 只係支持警察 <br />\n紅絲 愛國愛黨<br />\n<br />\n其實藍絲入面 都好多都唔中意大陸<br />\n只係唔知道自己俾紅絲利用緊<br />\n所以藍絲並不等於紅絲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而大家街上見到既獅子狗 癈老 係紅絲<br />\n<br />\n所以我地黃絲既敵人係共黨 係紅絲<br />\n依家可以做既係要向大陸文宣<br />\n喚醒果啲憎恨中共既所有人 同我地同行<br />\n只有支爆 我地先會勝利<br />\n<br />\n天滅中共 <br />\n光復香港時代革命 <br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"ca5cc5378a75224a4d6a637723fffe159fbabbe4","tid":1559781,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:14:19.000Z","msg":"敵人的朋友就是敵人"},{"pid":"f86fea8eeb5ecaa587f1fc5a97fd116447ccf1fa","tid":1559781,"uid":45160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:21:46.000Z","msg":"對家咁撚鍾意分化, 就用返同一招啦"},{"pid":"88eb15ffb532eb5e53344ae38839fc4e2a34dff3","tid":1559781,"uid":178470,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"係呀，班藍絲狗淨係鍾意暴力<br />\n但叫佢奶共返大陸住用大陸嘢就話不了"},{"pid":"e18b9ca554fd301e9bbc0886465d49b3b9e38b4b","tid":1559781,"uid":206298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca5cc5378a75224a4d6a637723fffe159fbabbe4","tid":1559781,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:14:19.000Z","msg":"敵人的朋友就是敵人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:29:11.000Z","msg":"冇錯 所以要將紅藍分割 逐一擊破"},{"pid":"7493c6189ac65c2eec83ee8676c62406a07bd563","tid":1559781,"uid":259521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T03:37:14.000Z","msg":"之前有篇野分析藍絲心態搵唔番"},{"pid":"8ea81dcbcb378d65d254b254d54813639c82a21a","tid":1559781,"uid":206298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7493c6189ac65c2eec83ee8676c62406a07bd563","tid":1559781,"uid":259521,"like":